description	"Revan

^2Weaponry:
- Revan's Lightsaber
-- Yellow / Red / Blue Styles
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Gun Defense   (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump  (2)
- Push  (3)
- Speed (2)
- Lightning (1)

^8Attributes:
- BP Free Jumps
- Force Block (1)
- Force Focus (1)

Formerly Darth Revan, his one time apprentice Darth Malak turned on him during battle, resulting in Revan's capture and mind wipe. Rebuilding his abilities with the Force, a different man emerged, one who shunned the Dark Side. To restore peace to the Republic, he must now face down and destroy his former student."